articles.author: UI-Glenn
articles.description:
Overview
UniFi Access Point 6.6.36 adds 6GHz support to several new countries that have adopted the WiFi6E standard. It's only available for Gen6 Access Points.
This release has been promoted to Stable/Official for the models listed below, it's still a Release Candidate for the others.

U6-Mesh
U6-IW
U6-Enterprise-IW

Improvements

Added 6GHz support to several new countries that have adopted the WiFi6E standard.
Fixed incorrect channels being used in outdoor mode.
Improved firmware update resiliency.
Improved overall range by enabling dynamic bandwidth support.
Improved overall stability by fixing kernel crashes.
Improved wireless uplink stability.
Improved range by increasing maximum TX power in FCC countries.
Fixed band steering occasionally not steering dual-band clients from 2.4GHz toâ€¦
articles.title: UniFi Access Point 6.6.36
